  "texts": [
    "In this paper, different feature aggregation operations are also studied, as shown in Figure 5C, the model performance is improved fast where the embeddings of semantic and structural networks are concatenated.",
    "However, the model uses the fusion approach of averaging and summing methods to lead to performance degradation as the increasing number of convolutional layers, when the number of graph convolutional layer is 16, the model performance decreases the most, especially the summing method.",
    "The simple concatenation operation continuously improves the model performance as the increasing number of graph convolutional layers, and the model performs best when the number of graph convolutional layer reaches 8.",
    "When the number of convolutional layer reaches 16, its performance is the best.",
    "Therefore, this paper uses concatenation method to fuse semantic features and structural features."
